src/fractal_multifractal.cpp (mfdma)  (clean-room reimplementation from
the published algorithm — not a translation of licensed source)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------
Algorithm: Gu GF, Zhou WX. Detrending moving average algorithm for
multifractals. Phys Rev E 2010;82:011136.

A MATLAB reference implementation was consulted during development
(MFDMA_1D.m; no license header present in the source file). The segment-
fluctuation core was validated against a Python transliteration of that
reference on synthetic test data (exact match to displayed precision).

